 camcorder. It doesn&#39;t have a lot of features like some of the best HD camcorders. There is no internal memory, 3D lens or integrated Wi-Fi. However, if those features don&#39;t interest you, the Polaroid iD879 doesn&#39;t make you pay for them. This device does have basic features such as intelligent auto. With intelligent auto you will not have to decide what camcorder setting you will need as it picks the settings that are optimal for your lighting situation and other factors. It also comes in a couple of color options if you don&#39;t feel like being chained down to standard black.","Polaroid&#39;s customer service is pretty average compared to manufacturers of the best HD camcorders. Polaroid offers email and phone support, as well as a small FAQs section. A live chat would be a welcome addition to the help and support offerings for Polaroid camcorders."]},"id":"7648e0f3-179b-4256-8c63-edbc54b8647a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"ce61b35f-6906-409b-b64c-e1b6d060ca58","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Polaroid use to be wildly popular with its instant photograph technology, so it is sad to see that they have not kept up with the trends in emerging technology. The Polaroid iD879 is a subpar HD video camcorder that barely does the basics in video shooting. But if you&#39;re looking around for a camcorder that doesn&#39;t have all those extra features you won&#39;t be using, then there is no reason to look past the Polaroid iD879."]},"id":"f75e8fde-a5c6-4a88-887d-321a1827cea9","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_56399","url":"/polaroid-id-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"anna-burleson","url":"/author/anna-burleson","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Anna Burleson","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"4bFWMi8qjrUwQuwAFnJjZM","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-05-15T18:12:37Z","datePublished":"2013-05-15T18:12:37Z","name"